[div class=p 
	[em 
		"Rockman no Constancy
	]em
	" is a very extensive ROM hack of 
	[em 
		"Mega Man 2
	]em
	", with changes to the music, the graphics, the level design, and the characters. A couple of the powerups from the original game remain, which means that a number of techniques that can be done there can also be done here.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Two versions of this hack exist: "normal" mode and "hard" mode, with the primary difference being no mercy invincibility on hard mode. 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/CUI 
		"CUI
	]a
	" here plays on "hard" mode and improves on the previous "hard" run by 80 seconds by making extensive use of zipping and death glitches.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"WARNING
	]b
	": There are instances of flashing lights during and after the Wily Stage boss fights, which may cause epileptic seizures to people affected.
